    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable ride and it\u2019s honestly been such a dream to own. It's in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to go and won't let you down. It runs smoothly and still looks great\u2014I'm sure you're going to love it as much as I have! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look or have any questions!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system recently serviced for optimal cam phasing. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential. The chassis has undergone a proactive rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high torque loads. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics, paired with staggered Style 67 alloys. With a linear power delivery and precise hydraulic steering, this M3 offers a pure mechanical connection that modern electronic racks cannot replicate. Well-maintained and sorted for the next enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Reliable engine. Clean interior. Regular maintenance performed. Ready for immediate use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a keen eye might find a few minor stone chips from highway miles\u2014purely cosmetic and consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple with only light natural creasing, and every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system, operates exactly as it should. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, a testament to a life of on-time oil changes and preventative maintenance. It has been recently inspected and fitted with a fresh set of premium all-season tires and new brake pads. This car has been my pride and joy, and it shows in the tight handling and composed ride quality. I have the complete service history available for your review to ensure total peace of mind.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a harmonious balance of performance and reliability. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and interior refinement. It stands as a testament to diligent ownership, featuring a clean aesthetic and a smooth, authoritative driving profile. Ideal for the professional seeking a dependable yet sophisticated automotive solution, this vehicle represents a significant value proposition in today's market.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a fantastic car. It's in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me. It drives smooth, looks great, and is ready to hit the road with a new owner! If you're looking for a reliable vehicle that's been well-loved and well-kept, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit boasts a documented VANOS service and comprehensive subframe reinforcement, addressing the chassis's primary weak points. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with precision, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The suspension has been refreshed with polyurethane trailing arm bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the 50/50 weight distribution remains communicative through the corners. An honest, high-performance driver\u2019s car with excellent drivetrain integrity and a redline that remains as exhilarating as ever.",
